\newlabel{fig:kg_covid}{{14}{11}{Knowledge graph for Post-COVID period. Supply chain and labor market disruptions become central causal nodes. Reflects major shift in policy discourse. 14 nodes, 31 edges}{figure.caption.15}{}}
